@sriharipotter and I made this mashup last year for my brother & sister-in-law’s Telugu & Gujarati wedding in order to represent the mixing of cultures. My side of the family did a whole dance to it at the sangeeth as well :) We have been meaning to release for over a year now but here it is, finally! Full song is available on @sriharipotter ‘s SoundCloud 🎼 

“Butta Bomma X Shubhaarambh”
Music, Mix & Master: @sriharipotter 
Vocals: @manisha.eerabathini 

Original Music Credits

@musicthaman @armaanmalik @ramjowrites @itsamittrivedi @shrutipathak27 @aslidivyakumar @swanandkirkire
